<p><span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">为加强我院各班级宣传工作的深入开展，促进各班争创先进良好局面，经济管理学院融媒体协会于5点40分在A10-115召开优秀宣传班级及宣传先锋动员会议，经济管理学院22级各班宣传委员参加会议，信息部部长程萱主持会议。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/2n18Qa8gmEI7X41P0XlVouE8GCy2GGKAh68lLlrurEpftp9fkweWQlSPcVViccpEIS1r0Vhlicr0KNegcy3a9WWQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&wxfrom=13&tp=wxpic" width="267" height="200" style="width: 267px; height: 200px;"/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 2.5px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; line-height: 37px; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">会议中，信息部部长程萱讲述了各班所要做的一些宣传工作，如班级照片挑选上传、班级视频或文章投稿工作的开展，班级微信公众号的开通等。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 2.5px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; line-height: 37px; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">以下是部分会议重点：</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 2.5px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; line-height: 37px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">（一）每班宣传委员于每周日晚10点前在群相册上传相应有效素材。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 2.5px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 37px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; caret-color: red; font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">（二）于宣传委员会议，及时参加，无故缺席每次扣5分。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 2.5px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 37px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; caret-color: red; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">（三）&nbsp;对于各项工作要求，认真完成。未及时完成次扣2分，提前且优秀完成工作可酌情加3-5分。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 2.5px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; line-height: 37px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">（四）学期末学院评选出“优秀宣传班级”3个以及“宣传先锋”3名，并颁发相应奖状和奖品，“宣传先锋”可凭借奖状加25学分。</span></p><p><br/></p>